                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="small text-muted mb-2">Built with:</p>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled small">
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Node.js & Express</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Bootstrap 5</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Chart.js for visualizations</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Pure JavaScript (no frameworks)</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Responsive design</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
